Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.41,0:01:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒的戒指哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.15,0:02:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是普通的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是發誓永遠的愛的訂婚戒指哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.82,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訂婚戒指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.35,0:02:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 男人向女人求婚時\N送給女性的訂婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要套入左手無名指的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 在七月七日的七夕節\N贈送更有效果哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 生為女人\N真該接受一次心上人的贈禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.67,0:02:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事 劍心\N為什麼叫我來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.15,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜是七夕\N阿薰 我要給你這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.50,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要對你發誓永遠不變的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們結婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.35,0:03:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 不行 那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.67,0:03:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你怎麼了\N振作點呀 阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振用點 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像在說什麼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像腦充血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她太想不開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她與劍心的關係\N好像一直沒什麼進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 該輪到我來幫她一個忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也算是為了阿薰的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了阿薰的幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在明天的七夕決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要撮合這個兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.55,0:04:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十六話\N阿薰感動不已  劍心的求婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訂婚戒指啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 大清早的你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去釣魚了 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 劍心\N你是不是忘記什麼重要的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼這麼大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 怎麼忘記重要的餌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是餌啦 今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.87,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是…\N確實是很好的釣魚日子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有自知之明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.68,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道劍心不可能\N在七月七日送我訂婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是至少今晚\N應該跟我一起看星星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.92,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心這種人\N自己成為魚餌被吃掉算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的門戶大開了\N好了 禰彥 再攻過來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.23,0:05:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我這種閉月羞花的少女\N平時只能一再的練劍道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 是我不該發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.35,0:06:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快冰敷一下\N要是骨裂就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你講得太誇張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去拿手巾過來\N你在這裏等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天禰彥這麼細心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上一隻魚也沒釣到\N看來今天是不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰冰涼涼的 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是剛汲上來的井水嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 我順便幫你揉肩膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.02,0:06:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼 平時你不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.12,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我經常受你的照顧\N老實說 心裏很感激呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是津南送給我的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.54,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到小姐喜歡甜食就拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送給我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是難得有蛋糕\N大家一起吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.74,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不用了 那是給阿薰的\N阿薰你吃就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去端茶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥跟左之助今天特別體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.33,0:07:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平時左之助總是待我像小孩\N看不起我 其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生都會故意欺負喜歡的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我有劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且連禰彥…他年紀太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 美麗是罪惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哭什麼 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.56,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為因為頭一次有人對我這麼溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 禰彥\N我的年紀比你大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們永遠是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友？那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把花瓶摔破了\N我們是好朋友 你會原諒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.81,0:08:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我最喜歡的花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.05,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是好朋友\N你就大人大量原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有 你也大人大量\N順便借我一些錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在「紅牛」債台高築了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天對少女而言\N是最重要的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的一天？什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…什麼朋友\N只會講有利於自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心裏已經有劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天釣到大魚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是阿薰的特別日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.19,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我釣到慶祝時用的\N帶頭尾的魚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別的日子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 劍心\N你為此一早去釣魚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 有什麼不對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道還對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶頭尾的啊 那真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.25,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 快抹鹽烤來吃了吧\N這條鯰魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰好像不喜歡鯰魚的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你不想出更貼心的禮物\N我的計劃會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來討債的呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事以後再談\N現在我有更重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有什麼硬硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要求不多\N不是非要鯛魚才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.13,0:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在閉月差花的少女\N的浪漫日子裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有人送鯰魚的 鯰魚！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽好了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天對阿薰而言是特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別的日子\N必需送特別的東西才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.11,0:10:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好現在\N你手中有個特別的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那東西送給她\N一切就順利平安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是拿撿來的東西送人\N不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了 要把戒指\N套入阿薰的指頭哦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.14,0:10:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以開門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.15,0:11:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把這個送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧…不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個…不是在作夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是訂婚戒指呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意假裝不知道\N還捉鯰魚來給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心太容易害羞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.24,0:11:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你準備了\N這麼好的戒指了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心真是 把人急死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個醜女在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怕啦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 急死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心你不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也不該在禰彥他們面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,套上無名指了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 謝謝你的訂婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快成為緋村薰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.92,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是結婚後他是住在這裏\N應該算是入贅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…是他改姓為神谷劍心了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.46,0:12:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活心流與御劍流湊在一起\N我們的孩子要繼承哪邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是活心流好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要是女兒的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以劍心與我的外貌\N女兒一定長得美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定會成為演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.54,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想等洗完衣服以後再打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家事是我的工作嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼事都不必做\N只要坐在這裏當老爺就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.36,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 明天我去學作菜好了\N好事不能多磨嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大掃除大掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.30,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰要下廚？\N是不是什麼大事的前兆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我也來釣今晚的菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詩織 事到如今\N我只好以死謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要自殺的話到別處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然看到你淹死慘狀\N我連睡覺醒來都會難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太傻了 原諒我 詩織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被喜歡的女人甩了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我把要送給她的\N重要的戒指丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說來也算有緣\N告訴我詳情好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.19,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有個女朋友\N我們立過山盟海誓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是幾天前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詩織   慎二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到詩織別有喜歡的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 這破東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來才知道那男人\N只是她分開十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然遇見的童年玩伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誤會都冰釋了\N戒指又有什麼重要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.43,0:15:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是外人不知道\N那是為了在今天向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拚命工作才買到的訂婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也一直期待這天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有找嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.97,0:15:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 我到河裏\N尋找丟掉的戒指好幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是連影子都沒找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子別說是訂婚了\N我對不起她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好以死謝罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 問你一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那戒指是不是\N上面有青色石頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.56,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 那是她誕生石藍寶石\N請問…你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之…恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏等著就對了\N不准尋短見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我會追到黃泉酷刑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.04,0:15:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 大事不好了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說那個人丟掉的戒指\N是鯰魚吐出來的戒指嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟阿薰說明原因\N請她還給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 事情沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.07,0:16:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.77,0:16:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳細的問站在那邊的女人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.97,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不曉得戒指\N竟有那麼深的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.58,0:16:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說劍心是向阿薰求婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.02,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不知道西洋的風俗\N並不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是七夕\N這時間太不巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.43,0:16:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…以為今天是阿薰的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我想看阿薰高興的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才設計這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實阿薰生日是六月啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以阿薰那麼高興呀\N她畢竟是女人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.71,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是如何不傷及她的女人心\N的情況下把戒指要回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且要在今天之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.12,0:17:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們自己想辦法好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次看都是那麼的漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來給我訓練吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天你特別有心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那無所謂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.51,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對 以後不能光是陪你了\N只有趁這時候多給你特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 這次我要用柔道進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然劍術上比不過你\N可是這個的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 比柔道的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷話心流柔術 木葉返
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要這樣才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來還有這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活心流的奧義是活人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.89,0:18:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有劍也要能應戰\N因此還融合了柔道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒聽說有這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.69,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 回應你的要求\N今天要給你紮實的特訓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫停呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是地獄旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴二段摔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 水溫如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了 你慢慢洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的應該沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結婚的話可以偶爾一起洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相替對方洗背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊～羞羞羞～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.43,0:19:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐洗澡的時候\N應該有把戒指脫下來放在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 要好好尋找哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…別慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不管阿薰再怎麼丑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不想碰年輕女人的腰帶啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.58,0:19:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是說那種話的時候\N動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.31,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是武士明神禰彥耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼無恥的事我幹不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思\N意思是我這個人無恥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.69,0:19:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想出這個方法的人是你\N那你自己動手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙說包在我身上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼 變態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.94,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.71,0:19:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 剛才抱歉抱歉\N我在找東西啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.82,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…洗完澡以後喝杯涼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟「紅牛」的小妙要來的啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說西方人習慣\N洗完澡後一口氣喝光這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個不會是酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.54,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點酒不算什麼\N今天是好日子不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次絕對成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快行動啊 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很癢的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動啦 醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什麼 笨手笨腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.83,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 左之助\N我記得阿薰的酒癖很差哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽到我在說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.88,0:21:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（神谷活心流醉拳）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應付不來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.46,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是劍心不對\N不該釣到吃下訂婚戒指的鯰魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃下什麼東西的鯰魚呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.70,0:21:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不行了 阿薰 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實情是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人命關天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 乖乖把戒指還給人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子萬一自殺了\N我們也有責任呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 失禮了  左之助 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼緊 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋轉看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 脫不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 禰彥 去拿鉗子來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說喝醋身體會軟\N你去拿醋來給小姐喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不行  拔不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼套進去的東西\N拔不出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.35,0:22:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰平日練劍鍛練\N所以手指比普通女性粗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.25,0:22:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是手指粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.46,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.99,0:22:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了 你看 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.30,0:22:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是受傷的功德呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.84,0:22:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你  托福我才能順利訂婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.08,0:22:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彥次郎 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.82,0:22:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你們幸福\N下次別再扔掉戒指哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 那兩人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.82,0:22:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了一邊 壞了一邊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我沒有女人味\N只會吃 既然這樣我要自暴自棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.93,0:22:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃…吃死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐心情差到極點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.57,0:23:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候男人要更體貼才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.44,0:23:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天這個日子\N就是為此而存在的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.11,0:23:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.75,0:23:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.32,0:23:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲到兩個月的生日禮物\N祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.32,0:23:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在才講生日快樂\N沒什麼感覺啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.23,0:23:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心快講「我不是那意思」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦 不必那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.27,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.34,0:23:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事身邊的人嘍嗦也沒用\N所以最好別去管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.61,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是…禰彥跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.62,0:23:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不行 女人的青春短暫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.12,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我一定要成功\N阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.27,0:24:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也去看一下傷口好了

